            <Image src={locationIcon} alt="" />
            <h3 class="font-header-3">Convenient Location</h3>
            <p class="reason-description reveal-text no-scrub">
              Located in the heart of <span class="fw-bold"
                >Washington D.C.</span
              >, Ahadu Global Network is easily accessible. Our convenient
              location means you can focus on your project, not your commute.
            </p>
          </div>

